{"tid":553223,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（求安慰）我以後唔養狗啦","createTime":"2018-02-07T08:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T13:57:08.000Z","uid":44509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f820d5e27ed355374e0e38e08af361ea07ce1937","tid":553223,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"醫左4個月都醫唔好<br />\n今朝，見佢冇力起身，訓係度柯<br />\n我番工邊做野邊流下男兒淚<br />\n老細叫我早走，陪到佢最後<br />\n見住佢走好心痛<br />\n<br />\n我個心就快頂唔住"},{"pid":"b3c423d01bc6cd72504d305c8c1c79af3edcca68","tid":553223,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f820d5e27ed355374e0e38e08af361ea07ce1937","tid":553223,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"醫左4個月都醫唔好<br />\n今朝，見佢冇力起身，訓係度柯<br />\n我番工邊做野邊流下男兒淚<br />\n老細叫我早走，陪到佢最後<br />\n見住佢走好心痛<br />\n<br />\n我個心就快頂唔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗死左一個月有多，一諗起佢都會喊"},{"pid":"3d3aa8e6ae375e54e88dbf686f5e3e0f604acce0","tid":553223,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">💪🏻</span>"},{"pid":"ac14d83f4839929a79077cff60723f802df67d27","tid":553223,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"我男人老狗 第一次喊成咁<br />\n喊到個人好攰<br />\n個世界好靜，好空虛"},{"pid":"662ed60022080001c504a8f9084c7eb9ac3b2dc2","tid":553223,"uid":131337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/173517_ab8fd9606255bfc266d11fb3b080a6a5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F173517_ab8fd9606255bfc266d11fb3b080a6a5.jpeg&h=21e56cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06857191e2d29043e0205f00cbea901dc717b812","tid":553223,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"8d2ce375ac51ba21e572f2ce264a4e3f6670a6b2","tid":553223,"uid":119378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"經歷過，喊到收唔到幸，以後唔會再養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他是我的唯一"},{"pid":"87704edadc0406c00edd66cea83187459e10b8dd","tid":553223,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"要好好記住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c462f5479e24b9a9689c31ad5b55318a6dc2c508","tid":553223,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 你老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293d06a9fd56cf6e90c020a3a2ac73d114371302","tid":553223,"uid":108756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"我經歷過四隻狗離開 四隻有兩隻出生就養 兩隻又好細隻就養 一齊大 可以話會有唔捨得 但其實又無咩野 因為我永遠有一句說話 people die we move on 訓醒又係一日 生活仍然繼續 你可以將佢地放係心 你可以用記憶去想念佢地 但你同時亦可以選擇睇得好化 甚至令自己無咩感覺 因為我覺得係選擇來 <br />\n所以我自己來講其實無咩野 任何生命都有死既一日 何況正常情況 狗一定比人類短 咁有咩好傷心 可以話係預左 但依家呢刻既我 我唔會再養狗"},{"pid":"86e6b0e58a7145ee5bb1d7771e27694ec67e886c","tid":553223,"uid":73131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"樓主我都有養狗 未經歷過佢地死亡 我都好驚有咁既一日 我只可以講如果佢地走左咪當佢地解脫 唔好再痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79068738167983cb55cd461d3e81acde325f2e6a","tid":553223,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e6b0e58a7145ee5bb1d7771e27694ec67e886c","tid":553223,"uid":73131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"樓主我都有養狗 未經歷過佢地死亡 我都好驚有咁既一日 我只可以講如果佢地走左咪當佢地解脫 唔好再痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"屌我都係唔想面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我隻狗仲要係狗場救出黎 好乖好痴我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f476d01a333c316511584516376a6b17c752414b","tid":553223,"uid":73131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79068738167983cb55cd461d3e81acde325f2e6a","tid":553223,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e6b0e58a7145ee5bb1d7771e27694ec67e886c","tid":553223,"uid":73131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"樓主我都有養狗 未經歷過佢地死亡 我都好驚有咁既一日 我只可以講如果佢地走左咪當佢地解脫 唔好再痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"屌我都係唔想面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我隻狗仲要係狗場救出黎 好乖好痴我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"我個隻兩歲先入我地屋企 家下六歲 希望佢可以長命百歲 之前佢整傷左隻腳擔心到我想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dae03d56f39854632e72735529d1297e19f26e8","tid":553223,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"我呀妹 成日都想佢陪佢一齊嫁<br />\n事到如今，我呀妹無時無刻都喊緊。<br />\n作為主人，我覺得我好無能....."}]}